'''手力雄神社'''
*千葉県館山市の神社（たぢからおじんじゃ）。[[手力雄神社 (館山市)]]を参照。 *岐阜県岐阜市の神社（てぢからおじんじゃ）。[[手力雄神社 (岐阜市)]]を参照。 *岐阜県各務原市の神社（てぢからおじんじゃ）。[[手力雄神社 (各務原市)]]を参照。
{{aimai}}

'''Tajikarao Shrine''' (手力雄神社) is a [[Shinto shrines]] enshrining [[Ama-no-Tajikarao|Ama-no-Tajikarao no Kami]]. Multiple shrines with the same name exist.
* {{ill|Tajikarao Shrine (Tateyama)|ja|手力雄神社 (館山市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (たぢからおじんじゃ) - Located in [[Chiba Prefecture]], [[Tateyama City]]. * {{ill|Tajikarao Shrine (Gifu City)|ja|手力雄神社 (岐阜市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (てぢからおじんじゃ) - Located in [[Gifu Prefecture]], [[Gifu City]]. * {{ill|Tajikarao Shrine (Kakamigahara)|ja|手力雄神社 (各務原市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (てぢからおじんじゃ) - Located in Gifu Prefecture, [[Kakamigahara City]]. * {{ill|Tajikarao Shrine (Ōgaki)|ja|手力雄神社 (大垣市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (てぢからおじんじゃ) - Located in Gifu Prefecture, [[Ōgaki City]]. * {{ill|Tajikarao Shrine (Nara City)|ja|手力雄神社 (奈良市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (たぢからおじんじゃ) - Located in [[Nara Prefecture]], [[Nara City]]. * {{ill|Tajikarao Shrine (Sakurai)|ja|手力雄神社 (桜井市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (たぢからおじんじゃ) - Located in Nara Prefecture, [[Sakurai City]]. == See Also ==
Shrines enshrining Ama-no-Tajikarao no Kami: * {{ill|Haseyamaguchi Shrine|ja|長谷山口坐神社|12=draft|12=draft}} (Located in [[Nara Prefecture]], [[Sakurai City]]). * {{ill|Togakushi Shrine|ja|戸隠神社|12=draft|12=draft}} (Located in [[Nagano Prefecture]], [[Nagano City]]). * {{ill|Sana Shrine|ja|佐那神社|12=draft|12=draft}} (Located in [[Mie Prefecture]], [[Taki District]]). * {{ill|Shirai Shrine (Amagasaki)|ja|白井神社 (尼崎市)|12=draft|12=draft}} (Located in [[Hyōgo Prefecture]], [[Amagasaki City]]). * {{ill|Oyama Shrine (Tateyama)|ja|雄山神社|12=draft|12=draft}} (Located in [[Toyama Prefecture]], [[Kamiichi Town]] in [[Nakaniikawa District]]). * {{ill|Subsidiary Shrines|ja|摂末社|12=draft|12=draft}} of Togakushi Shrine and Togakushi Sha. * {{ill|Togami Shrine|ja|戸明神社|12=draft|12=draft}} (Located in [[Fukuoka Prefecture]], [[Kitakyūshū City]]).
